::Spears:

Her trainer program on survival mode, she stormed off, away from 
Firearm and Lunarpine. "NO way your getting me into stasis lock so 
you can poke and prod on me. No way buster. No sir. I am not going to 
turn into anyone's science experiment.  uh uh. No way on this 
planet.  It's not going to happen if I got anything to say about it."

Then her maximal program took over the trainer program.  She stopped 
dead in her tracks and her body shook.  She then turned her head, 
looking for Firearm and Lunarpine. "Hey, were did you guys go?" She 
turned and saw them up ahead of her going towards the Cybertron 
Fire. "Hey, what did you guys do, run ahead of me?"  She took a few 
steps forward and then stopped.  The trainer program took over again.
Each time the programs fought, the trainer program got stronger and 
starting to over power her maximal program. Her body shook as she 
stood there.  Then she looked at the bots. "Sorry, no can stay and 
get cut up.  Got to go guys."  She turned away from then and started 
running.
